Class RandomSynthesizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.solvers.RandomSynthesizer

    Synthesizer

    public class RandomSynthesizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Synthesizer
    A synthesizer that uar picks a new candidate program. There is no guarantee that each candidate will be unique. This should never be used in a real system; it is for testing only.
